title: Tom Brady, Joel Embiid, Dak Prescott, and Russell Westbrook
itunes:title: Tom Brady, Joel Embiid, Dak Prescott, and Russell Westbrook
description:
Colin discusses the growing possibility of QB Tom Brady leaving the Patriots, why he feels the 76ers should keep G Ben Simmons over C Joel Embiid, why the Cowboys would replace QB Dak Prescott with Brady, and why he isn't impressed with the recent success of G Russell Westbrook in Houston. Guests include Nick Wright, Greg Cosell, and Chris Jones.
